Package action.DoctorActions

Class CreateAppointmentOutcomeAction

java.lang.Object
action.DoctorActions.CreateAppointmentOutcomeAction
All Implemented Interfaces:
DoctorAction
public class CreateAppointmentOutcomeAction extends Object implements DoctorAction
Represents an action to create and store an outcome record for a completed appointment.

This action allows doctors to document key details of the appointment, including consultation notes, prescribed medications, and follow-up requirements. It interacts with the DoctorAppointmentController to retrieve appointment details, and uses the AppointmentOutcomeManager to persist the outcome record.
